## Technical SEO Checklists

### Crawlability Checklist
- [ ] robots.txt exists and is valid
- [ ] XML sitemap exists and is submitted to GSC
- [ ] No important pages blocked by robots.txt
- [ ] Canonical tags are correct and consistent
- [ ] No redirect chains (max 1 redirect hop)
- [ ] 404 pages return proper 404 status codes
- [ ] Hreflang implemented for multilingual sites
- [ ] Internal linking structure is deep (max 3 clicks from homepage)

### Core Web Vitals Checklist
- [ ] LCP element identified and optimized
- [ ] Images have explicit width/height attributes
- [ ] Critical CSS is inlined
- [ ] Fonts use `font-display: swap`
- [ ] JavaScript is deferred/async where possible
- [ ] Third-party scripts are lazy loaded
- [ ] CDN is configured for static assets
- [ ] Server response time < 200ms (TTFB)

### On-Page SEO Checklist
- [ ] Single H1 per page containing primary keyword
- [ ] Title tag 50–60 characters
- [ ] Meta description 120–155 characters with CTA
- [ ] Images have descriptive alt text
- [ ] URL is short, descriptive, uses hyphens
- [ ] Internal links use descriptive anchor text
- [ ] Page has at least one relevant outbound link
- [ ] Content is at least 300 words (informational: 1000+)
- [ ] Primary keyword in first 100 words
- [ ] Structured data is implemented and valid

