## Performance Monitoring KPIs

Track these weekly:
```
Organic Traffic          → Google Analytics 4 (Sessions, Users)
Keyword Rankings         → Google Search Console (Avg. Position)
Click-Through Rate       → Google Search Console (CTR by page)
Core Web Vitals          → GSC > Core Web Vitals report
Indexed Pages            → GSC > Index Coverage
Backlinks                → Ahrefs/Moz/Semrush
Domain Authority         → Moz DA / Ahrefs DR
Page Speed               → PageSpeed Insights API
```

