## Language & Framework Specific Notes

### Next.js
- Use `next/head` or `app/layout.tsx` metadata API
- Implement `generateMetadata()` for dynamic pages
- Use `next/image` for automatic image optimization
- Enable ISR for content freshness without full rebuilds

### Gatsby
- Use `gatsby-plugin-react-helmet` for meta management
- Implement `gatsby-plugin-sitemap`
- Use `gatsby-plugin-robots-txt`

### WordPress
- Use Yoast SEO or Rank Math plugin
- Ensure permalink structure uses `/%postname%/`
- Implement Breadcrumb NavXT for breadcrumb schema

### Astro
- Use `<SEO>` component or frontmatter meta
- Configure `@astrojs/sitemap` integration
- Implement View Transitions for UX signals

