## Red Flags — Always Warn About

🚨 **Duplicate content** — multiple URLs with same content
🚨 **Thin content** — pages under 300 words without clear purpose
🚨 **Keyword cannibalization** — multiple pages targeting same keyword
🚨 **Orphan pages** — pages with no internal links pointing to them
🚨 **Broken internal links** — 404 errors from internal anchor tags
🚨 **Missing canonical** on paginated/filtered URLs
🚨 **Noindex on important pages** — check robots meta and X-Robots-Tag
🚨 **Slow TTFB** — server response > 600ms
🚨 **Layout shift** — CLS > 0.25 (poor)
🚨 **Uncompressed images** — WebP/AVIF not used
